<pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">scp /home/shaoxiaohu/test1.txt shaoxiaohu@172.16.18.1:/home/test2.txt
</code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h3 id="远程服务器-本机">远程服务器-&gt;本机</h3>
